---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import img1 from "../../images/services/img1.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<MainLayout title="Business Analysis">
  <div
    class="bg-detail-img bg-no-repeat h-96 w-full absolute top-0 grayscale -z-40"
  >
    <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-80 w-full h-full"></div>
  </div>
  <section class="mx-16 min-[1600px]:ml-32 flex text-white">
    <div class="mt-48 min-[1600px]:mt-72 gap-x-20">
      <header class="flex flex-col w-full items-center mb-72">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Creative</h2>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="h-full">
            <h2 class="text-5xl">
              The team at Digital & Design has full creative expertise to create
              stunning visuals and video content that sets your brand apart from
              competition.
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <Image src={img1} alt="img1" class="h-96 w-full object-fill" />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-2 gap-16">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Brand Identity</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Our team of visual communication specialists knows how to create
              brands that are visually striking and different. Our team creates
              the logos, brand colors, stationary, visual merchandising and
              other brand collateral. We are experts in creating strong brand
              identity for businesses and ensure all brand guidelines are set
              for future communication goals as well.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Storyboarding</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              The team has the ability of creating visual storyboards for your
              TVC/DVCs so that your brand and production house knows frame by
              frame what to follow when shooting the video.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Campaign Designing</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              We specialise in creating stunning key graphic visuals for your
              campaigns that include Static Lockups for Digital Ads, Adaptations
              of campaign imagery in multiple sizes for various touchpoints and
              also all forms of Website Visuals.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">TVC/DVC Production</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Our team has a vast experience of producing TVC and DVCs for
              brands to ensure your product is highlighted along with achieving
              the communication objective. From talent management, DOP to
              location and on the day operations, we handle it all.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Photo/Video Production & Editing</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              We take data from your business, the industry and the market to
              develop trends that will allow our team to create an entire
              forecast for your business to set a benchmark upon.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Social Media Content Design</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Our design team know how to carefully curate social media content
              to ensure clean and good aesthetics on your profile along with
              achieving your brandâ€™s communication goal.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
